            </Button>
        </Grid>
        <Grid HorizontalAlignment="Left" Height="240" Margin="88,322,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="727">
            <Label Content="DESCRIPTION:" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Height="30" Margin="16,33,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="129" Foreground="#FFFDFDFD" FontSize="16" FontWeight="Bold"/>
            <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" Height="139" Margin="20,78,0,0" TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="697" Foreground="#FFFFCE5C" FontSize="16" FontWeight="Bold" TextAlignment="Justify" Text="Getting Started with Advanced C# is a practical guide for developers who already have basic C# knowledge and want to level up. It covers advanced concepts such as LINQ, asynchronous programming, delegates, events, generics, and memory management. The book includes hands-on examples and real-world applications to strengthen understanding. Perfect for learners aiming to master C# for enterprise-level software development and .NET applications."/>
        </Grid>

    </Grid>
